text: When you call @FedEx and the customer support can't stop yawning or manage to speak coherently. Yes that. I thought they were supposed to be good.

@BearTowell Hi, this is April.  I'm sorry to learn of this experience.  I will be happy to assist.  Please DM your name, address, city, state, zip code, tracking number, phone number, and email address. https://t.co/7vnSkvqx3r
@FedExHelp Hi April, I have email Fedex Uk as the phone call was so bad to ensure the information has been passed on correctly.
@BearTowell You can also reach out to @FedExHelpEU for assistance in your location. https://t.co/6uE0yQ8ibI
